snippet.title: Johnny Depp's Exes & Amber's Assistant DESTROY Heard
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp's trial against The Sun for libel and defamation connected to Amber Heard has been going on in London. This week, Depp's ex-wife Vanessa Paradis, and ex-girlfriend Winona Ryder. along with others, including Kate James, Amber Heard's own assistant at the time during said allegations, all came forward to destroy Heard in court this week.
